Software Requirements
=====================

   GNU GCC 4.2.1
   GNU Libtool 2.4
   GNU Autoconf 2.65
   GNU Automake 1.11.1
   GNU Readline 6.1
   Git 1.7.2.3
   Driver Manager:
      iODBC 2.52.6 
      unixODBC 2.3.0


Tested Platforms
================

   FreeBSD 8.1
      - MyODBC 3.51.26
      - SQLite ODBC 0.88

   OS X 10.6.6
      - FileMaker xDBC 11.3.76
      - MyODBC 5.1.8
      - SQLite ODBC 0.88

   Slackware 13.1
      - MyODBC 5.1.8
      - SQLite ODBC 0.88


